Scores & Video is not just another live score app. Our ambition is to create the best second screen for football fans everywhere. Push notifications, video highlights, interactive polls and photos recreating the atmosphere of stadium - everything to enhance the experience of watching football once and forever. 

What you’ll get right now (and it’s only the beginning):

• instant scores & videos, of course;
• push notifications, reliable, fast and easily customized;
• live match feeds with lineups and tactical formations;
• more than 200 tournaments with easy-to-use tables, schedules and stats (and yes, you can choose only those you need);
• interactive polls - vote for the best and the worst players or make your prediction and compare it with the wisdom of the crowd;
• selected fans’ photos of everything around the game - wherever you may be, feel like you’re in the stands right now.

Available in English, Spanish, French, Italian, German, Dutch, Polish, Brazil Portuguese, Turkish, Indonesian, Malay and Russian.

Subscriptions for ads removal are $2.99 per month or $25.19 forever. Subscriptions will be charged to your iTunes account after your confirmation of purchase. Your monthly subscription will automatically renew each month and be charged through your iTunes account, subscription forever will be charged one time. You can turn off auto-renew at any time from your iTunes account settings. Cancellation of the current active subscription period is not allowed.

Also available on Apple Watch.

For more details on the application's privacy policy and terms of use please see: http://scoresandvideo.com/m/en/agreement/
